title: Starlight Girls - Converse Rubber Tracks: Track of the Week
description:
The single "Rock My World Events" by Starlight Girls is this week's "Track of the Week". The band came to Converse Rubber Tracks and experimented with sound, the studio set-up, and the overall instrumentation for their original track. Watch the four members of Starlight Girls record their original single "Rock My World Events" at Converse Rubber Tracks.

For more on Converse Rubber Tracks, check out:
www.converse.com/rubbertracks
